OL,3,CMastercard teams up with long-named
OL,4,Cplaces to promote quicker online
OL,5,Cpayments
OL,7,FMastercard said it will be giving
OL,8,Fdemonstrations of how the technology
OL,9,Fworks to residents of the community in
OL,10,FAnglesey, which is also known as
OL,11,FLlanfairpwllgwyngyll, Llanfairpwll or
OL,12,FLlanfair PG.
OL,14,FThe payments provider said the
OL,15,FLlanfairpwll community will become one
OL,16,Fof the first in Europe to try out the
OL,17,Ftime-saving technology, which allows
OL,18,Fshoppers to pay without the need to
OL,19,Fshare long card numbers with online
OL,20,Fretailers.
