OL,3,CMastercard teams up with long-named
OL,4,Cplaces to promote quicker online
OL,5,Cpayments
OL,7,FMastercard said a secure process
OL,8,Fcalled "tokenisation" replaces the
OL,9,Fcard number with random numbers, or
OL,10,Ftokens, for each transaction, which
OL,11,Fare meaningless if stolen. It added
OL,12,Fthat this protects consumers from
OL,13,Fscammers as well as retailers from
OL,14,Fcybersecurity and data breach threats.
OL,16,FConsumers can register their card with
OL,17,Fclick to pay on their banking app and
OL,18,Flook out for the click to pay icon at
OL,19,Fthe checkout.
