OL,7,FIts research indicates people take
OL,8,Fjust under three minutes on average to
OL,9,Fenter their address and payment
OL,10,Fdetails when shopping online.
OL,12,FA survey of 2,000 people across the UK
OL,13,Fby 3Gem, commissioned by Mastercard,
OL,14,Findicates nine in 10 (94%) shoppers
OL,15,Fpulled the plug on online purchases
OL,16,Flast year when they faced friction or
OL,17,Funwelcome surprises at the checkout.
